These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, august, november
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, green, coral, ivory
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, fishing, skydiving
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, game, swisher, dunhill
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who likes green##1
 5. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
 6. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 8. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the person who's birthday is in january##7
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
13. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | november    | april | august    | january   |
| Color   | mauve | coral | green | ivory |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks       | fishing   | skydiving  | baking     |
| Cigar     | old-henry      | swisher   | dunhill    | game    |

