.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, february, june
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, chef, nurse, dressmaker
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, hedgehog, hamster
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip, daffodil, bellflower
 1. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 3. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the frog##1
 5. the chef is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the owner of the frog##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
10. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
11. the owner of the mouse is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday          | may   | february       | june    | april      |
| Job   | bartender | dressmaker | chef         | nurse   |
| Pet   | hamster   | frog  | mouse       | hedgehog |
| Flower         | dahlia      | daffodil  | bellflower | tulip |

