.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
City: boston, marseilles, hamburg, hannover
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, house, folk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis, rose, iris
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving, sudoku, singing
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the fan house##5
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person traveling to boston and the fan house##7
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 5. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the fan dubstep##5
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is not the fan pop##6
 8. the fan house is not the person traveling to hannover##6
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the fan pop##3
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan folk##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the fan house##3
12. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| City           | hannover | boston | marseilles | hamburg |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep        | folk    | pop    | house    |
| Flower   | marigold        | iris   | amaryllis   | rose         |
| Hobby           | skydiving          | rock-climbing       | singing   | sudoku           |

