 4. the fan gospel is the person who likes coral##1
 5. the person playing chess is not the person who likes azure##6
 6. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan blues##5
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the person playing chess##7
 9. the person eating asparagus is the person who likes azure##1
10. the fan blues is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
11. the person eating apple is not the person who likes azure##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop | blues       | classical         | gospel       |
| Game         | chess     | monopoly    | snooker   | scrabble |
| Food           | cabbage   | asparagus | kale | apple     |
| Color   | purple      | azure          | lilac           | coral |

