 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 7. the person who likes yellow is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 8. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
10. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the pony and the person who likes orange##2
12. the person who likes brown is the owner of the dog##1

