 2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the pilot##1
 3. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
 4. the game-smoker is on the left of the designer##1
 5. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
 7. the pilot is somewhere between the wooden house and the gothic-revival house##7
 8. the photographer is not the wooden house##6
 9. the colonial house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
10. the person driving the bike is on the left of the game-smoker##1
11. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
12. the pilot is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Job         | coach      | pilot   | photographer   | designer       |
| Transport   | quad-bike | bike    | trike | boat       |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | siglo | game   | montecristo     |
| House         | wooden   | modern    | gothic-revival   | colonial |

