.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, canasta, bridge
City: liverpool, new-york, venice, hamburg
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, february, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, helicopter, van
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person driving the van and the person driving the helicopter##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is not the person driving the subway##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
 7. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person traveling to hamburg##7
 8. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to venice##1
12. the person traveling to venice is not the person driving the helicopter##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | billiard   | bridge     | canasta   | monopoly |
| City       | hamburg   | liverpool | new-york | venice    |
| Birthday      | february | august | june   | july  |
| Transport        | van | roller     | helicopter   | subway |

