4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, prince, swisher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, march, december
 1. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the american##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the owner of the chinchilla and the cain-smoker##2
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 4. the american is on the far right##1
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is not the prince-smoker##6
 7. the prince-smoker is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the hamster##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is not the owner of the hamster##6
 9. the swisher-smoker is not the owner of the rat##6
10. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is not the brazilian##6
13. the prince-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
14. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
