.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, gospel, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, nigerian, indonesian, pakistani
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, mah-jongg, chess
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, baccarat, davidoff
 1. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
 2. the indonesian is the fan gospel##1
 3. the swisher-smoker is the person playing chess##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the fan rock and the fan indie##2
 5. the polish is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5
 6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the indonesian and the fan house##7
 7. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
 8. the person playing monopoly is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
10. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
11. the baccarat-smoker is in an even position##4
12. the polish is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
